Why Perfective Software Maintenance Matters
 Perfective maintenance focuses on improving existing software functionality and performance without altering its core structure. By proactively addressing performance issues, optimizing workflows, and adding transformative functionalities, businesses can achieve higher efficiency, user satisfaction, and long-term reliability.
